f the scene.\r\n\r\n**B)** It establishes that a character is experiencing an internal conflict.\r\n\r\n**C)** It makes an assertion that the next sentence then expands on.\r\n\r\n**D)** It illustrates an idea that is introduced in the previous sentence.\r\n\r\n**Correct Answer:** D\r\n\r\n**Explanation:** The underlined sentence illustrates the idea introduced in the previous sentence, which is that the landscape reflects Lily's present mood. The detailed description of the landscape serves to emphasize this connection between her emotions and her surroundings.	\N
