hanges it requires in business models, consumer behavior, and policy frameworks.\r\n\r\nD) Incorrect: The passage mentions both governments and businesses exploring ways to incorporate circular economy principles, not just governments.\r\n\r\nThese detailed explanations should provide a clearer understanding of why each answer choice is correct or incorrect for all the questions in the document	\N
