ice provides general information about their fields but does not highlight their specific research contributions. B) Correct Answer. This choice effectively highlights the specific research contributions of both scientists and their potential implications. C) This choice mentions their research areas but does not emphasize their contributions as effectively as option B. D) This choice provides information about their research areas but does not highlight the contributions and potential implications as effectively as option B.\r\nThese examples should provide a comprehensive understanding of how to approach Notes questions on the Digital SAT.	\N
