ical implications of planting a flag on a summit:\r\n\r\nContext Fit: The passage briefly mentions planting a flag, but it is framed as a personal testament rather than a geopolitical act. The primary focus is on Tara's journey and achievement.\r\n\r\nTherefore, the correct answer is B) The physical and spiritual journey in conquering a mountain, as it encapsulates the central theme of Tara Singh's story as described in the passage.
