lity.\r\n\r\nTherefore, the sentence should read: "This mutualistic interaction is crucial for plant growth and soil health, demonstrating the complexity of ecosystem interdependencies. Therefore, these fungi are being studied for their potential to improve agricultural productivity and sustainability."
