d impact of climate change on species migration, leading to conservationists' call for climate mitigation efforts.\r\n\r\nTherefore, the sentence should read: "This shift can disrupt existing ecosystems and endanger species unable to adapt quickly enough. As a result, conservationists emphasize the need for climate mitigation efforts to preserve biodiversity."
